                <div class="col-span-7">
                    <p class="mb-7 text-xl/relaxed">Phat Scooters is a high-end electric scooter maker based in Phoenix, Arizona. In 2020, they adopted Nextiva to empower their customer support team to better serve their customers and improve their overall business decision-making</p>
                    <p class="text-base/loose opacity-70 mb-10">Founded in 2017, Phat Scooters selss high-end electric scooters to consumers around the world, servicing customers such as Bill Murray and Jeremy Renner. In Fall 2020, they began to search for an alternative business phone platform to their previous business phone provider, Verizon.</p><span class="mb-4 py-5 pl-5 pr-3.5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-content/10 via-content/10 to-content/0 font-light inline-flex items-center gap-1.5"><svg class="mb-0.5 w-4 md:w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
